e="margin:0 0 1em 0;">(c)  “Financial institution” includes any bank, savings and loan association, or other institution in this state, including a public agency, that regularly makes, arranges, or purchases loans for the purchase, construction, rehabilitation, improvement, or refinancing of housing accommodations.</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">(d)
